This paper discusses the development and design of conversational systems, specifically social chatbots, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI) technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.SD (Sound), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
